{"tid":735577,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【堅轉會】簽約3年 韋斯咸官宣韋舒亞加盟","createTime":"2018-07-09T14:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T07:47:20.000Z","uid":161311,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8022f03780a2003da6ef9827cc95fe799ab982f1","tid":735577,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"韋舒亞與韋斯咸簽約3年。<br />\n<br />\n韋斯咸官方網站宣佈，於上月尾約滿後離開阿仙奴的韋舒亞免費加盟，並與球隊簽約3年。<br />\n<br />\n這位26歲的前英格蘭國腳上月因與阿仙奴新帥艾瑪利就上陣時間未能達成共識，驅使他決定在合約完結後不再留隊，結束一共17年的阿仙奴歲月。而他本月回復自由身後，有多家球會均表示興趣，早前更傳出他將會加盟土超球會費倫巴治。然而他決定留在倫敦，最終選擇加盟韋斯咸。<br />\n<br />\n這位過去為阿仙奴於英超上陣125次的中場球員，將與韋斯咸簽約3年，薪酬則未有透露。而他將會在今日飛往瑞士，與新領隊柏歷堅奴及一眾隊友會合，開始季前操練。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180709/58422049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180709%2F58422049&d=bh1BcQ5rWyKJdpxLwFbo%2F8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=2a4a9438\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180709%2F58422049&h=c77fd14f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180709/58422049</a>"},{"pid":"14d24dcd5c66e92b3d89278c1a3e239a08b797f9","tid":735577,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"韋舒亞你條25仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa1a0263e6c9ed7926881b9345baa546c9383d4","tid":735577,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"煙剷"},{"pid":"f64b540fe200f82272ec21f12e770df66973caa2","tid":735577,"uid":15862,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"太子健健康康既話<br />\n鎚仔就真係開季笑撚到煞科"},{"pid":"b4a3ef96a51603b4309143d240875013c81f6bdb","tid":735577,"uid":163248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco